description: We’re moving on to the second elimination match of our 2014 Summer Smackdown Tournament. This week we have hung stud, Jay “Slick Dick” Rising facing off against seasoned kombatant, Eli “The Hammer” Hunter. Each fighter has a loss under their belt so knowing the taste of defeat makes them fight all the more harder. Hammer is relentless with his vicious leg locks but Slick-Dick manages to use his strength to slam his opponent hard to the mat. The championship gold belt is on the line, not to mention the bragging rights of being named tournament champion that come along with it. Watch as these two hung hunks fight balls to the wall for sexual domination!
title: Naked Kombat's Summer Smackdown Tournament - Match 2
